oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Ethel Adkins and upstairs tenant
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Ethel Adkins and an unidentified woman tenant on the steps of the Adkins family home at 819 Franklin Street. The Adkins rented upstairs rooms in their home to service members and other individuals during WWII.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Adkins, Ethel Darnell, 1892-1981; World War, 1939-1945; Apartment dwellers
